hey i hardly write in this thing so i'll write. lol what a motivation...yeh but i just graduated just tunred 18. crazy. high school is over. wow never thought that day would come but now it has. i'm not sad like the rest just want to live the rest of my life. i hope college is fun. it will be fun what the hell am i saying...lol but yeh

so now summer is upon us. so far its been bad ass. running, lifting weights. i have to get ready to play college ball. against guys who are better quicker faster than me. just have to work twice as hard if i want to make it. yeh for those of you'll who dont know. i'm going to college in fort worth to a skool called texas wesleyan. well i think i'm going because the college is real expensive so i'm looking at other alternatives for money. trying to get sponsershiops from businesses and stuff like that. so if u'll can help me in ne way just tell me. thanx. but ne ways yeh i'm going to yeh play basketball for them if i get a chance to go. but yeh,hopefully everything goes good for me. 

let me tell u'll about my day since it was pretty kool. 1st it started off waking up at 12, yessss i love waking up at 12, c'mon let me it was sunday. well ne ways woke up and ate a steak, a delicious steak might i add. but yes. then went over to my cousins house with my friend peter, and his friend marco. we played x-box, some tennis game, it was pretty bad ass. then we went on the four-wheelers and were playing this game. let me explain. we each have 4 tennis balls. and we have to hit the opponent. the guy thats driving is 1 point and the passenger is 2 points. and we played up to 5 points. man we killed, it was fun though. after that i had been wanting to play real tennis, so we got a group of friends and played tennis at the park. it was fun real bad ass.

i hope to have more summer days like this. but this is already long enough. i dont know who's gonna read or what not but if u do leave a comment. thanx. & bye.

i never update weekly but i had such a bad day i have to update today. today started off with me fallin alseep in the shower. omg how the hell does someone fall asleep in the shower. i'm too embarassed to discuss that. so i came to skool at the beginning of 3rd period. then i have to go to the counsler's because they sent me something in the mail that says they might put me on academic probation. then i didnt do my accounting work. and brittany didnt go to skool today so i was alone at lunch cuz she wasnt here. then my day got a little better, cuz accounting is due thursday instead of today. ozzy's hair looks kool, and she made me feel a little better cuz she actually cared about me to ask wut wuz wrong. then i watched a movie in english and it was sad but i liked it. finally after skool i went to the stc building and could not find where i needed to go. finally after 20 minutes i find it. cuz its a new building. i talk to the councler and she told me, last year i failed accounting. and my grade for this semester and last years two grades averages out to a 1.5, but my normal grade is a 4.0. so they sent me a letter to warn me to keep my grade up. so they took me off academic hold. so thats good. and i dont have to go to the banquette. so fuck it i'm gonna go to sleep and hope i have a better day tomorrow. HoLLa Peace up J down!!!

fuck we lost! my highschool basketball career is over! wtf am i going to do with my life. i was hoping this day would come later, but unfortunatlly it came tonight. now i have the rest of my life ahead of me. i have to play college basketball. i have to!

hey what's up! everything has been going good. javi is talking to jena now. i think that's cool. i mean if i can't get her, at least one of my best buddies is talking to her. i dont know if i'm talking to brittany because she has a boyfriend. it seems i always pick a girl with a boyfriend. she's bad ass we have so much in common and we can have an endless conversation about stupid shit. but i dont want to get in the middle with her and her boyfriend. but wutever happens happens. enough of the girl talk. on to basketball talk...lol
regular season went bad ass. now its play offs. this is the 1st time in my life i've been to playoffs. its weird but i'm excited but i don't feel excited. i dunno its weird. to all ya'll who read my journal and what not. go to our game tuesday @ harlingen 7:05 be there or be square, fo shizzle my damn nizzle. yup! the all star game was bad ass. a lot of bad ass dunks. they cant get up like me but they aight. lol! and damn the dunk contest was off the hook for real. daaaaaang josh smith up in the niaaaga!!! and you know he tight when he gots the name josh. for real it dont even matter the name gives it all away. but yeh holla to everyone. peace and i'm out of this motha fucka! peace up J down LaTe!

hey wuts up to everyone. weekend was pretty bad ass. didnt do ne thing special but it was still bad ass. i spent time with this girl i think i'm talking to but i'm not sure. but spendin time with her has been bad ass. i keep thinkin about that one girl though. its kraaaaaaazy. lol like i watched the movie "ray" yesterday and she told me she liked it a long time ago, and for some reason i thought of her. those are the little things that make me think of her. i sound all gay. lol. pinche queeer. lol but nah i 'm watchin some sweet 16 thing on mtv, daaaaamn these kids r freakin' rich, for real, i'm jealous of how rich they are. fuck a duck in a big black truck with the windows up going wut wut wut! lol ne time u wanna flo allison bring it, wuuuuuut i'll be rite here. lol LAte

SuperBowl Sunday. i really dont watch football but i like the halftime show so i guess i'll watch that. lol man i hate it when people do shit behind your back and u know about it. its eaither u be a man and fuckin tell the person or dont do it. but fuck it. now i dont know if i like this girl or not. a new girl. bad ass. she has a boyfriend though. lol i hate when i do this shit. always go for the girls with boyfriends. fuck it again. lol but she's bad ass, she has a personality like me. lol funnny as hell. lol but this other girl is still on my mind. why would she do what she does with my friend knowing deep inside i still have feelings for her. better yet why would my friend do that with the girl which he knows i still have feeligns for. wuts up with that. lol i'm watching the ending of troy becuz i never saw it. just thought i'd tell you'll lol. but thats all i have to say, and here's something i wrote lastnight for no paticular person.

                                                       a tear is shed for happiness
                                                        a tear is shed for sorrow
                                                      will u still love me tomorrow
                                                     i will just have to wait n see
                                                          do you really love me
                                                              i know you do
                                                          that is why i love you

i always seem never to write in this, even though most of the time i have a lot of feelings. i just hide them really well. but recently things have been going good. basketball is great. 8-1 damn thats a good record and we're in the playoff's for sure. i really want to get 1st though all we have to do is win out, sounds hard but i have faith. its crazy that i only have 4 guarenteed games 3 district and 1 playoff, more games but depending on if we win. but after that high school basketball for me is over. its a scary thought. for real. with girls, nothing has really happened. i got over amber which is bad ass, i mean she's cool and all but...na i wont say nothing she's just kool. but there's only one girl that i cant seem to forget about. and i'm not gonna mention her name becuz i just dont want to. but i never see her in school so i forget about her. but everytime i see her i dont know i feel somethings missin, like ther could be more. its a strange feeling. and sometimes i do want to feel that feeling and sometimes i dont. i dont know if i make sense but oh well. the thing that sux is i think she likes one of my best buddies. and then i'm talking to my ex the only real g/f i've ever had. i dont know if its talking to get into a relationship or just talking. and she's bad ass and everything. but i just dont know what i want. i dont know if its jealosy or wut but i wouldnt want to see that girl with my best friend. like thats a fucked up feeling i would have. aNd then i met a bad ass friend, and she's awesome like fun to talk too and everything. she likes me though. it doesnt bother me though. like i dont think i have feelings towards her but sometimes i dont know. i'm reading this shit over and i'm messed up. i dont know if u'll should know all this stuff about me or not. its pretty messed up that i'm talking about everything thats going on im my life for everyone to read. girls is the only part of my life that i have no control over. there always has to be something wrong. it never fails. i wish everything would be ok but doesnt everyone want that. damn i cant get that girl off my mind. it jus irrates the fuck out of me. but we'll see what happens in the future. everything happnes for a reason and i truely and stongly believe that. faith is the only thing i have.

considering i dont have a computer so i dont get to update in this as much as usual. so let me tell you wut has been going on in my life. the more recent one i'll tell you about...kinda sad? well my whole life, i have no idea what is wrong with me but i always like a girl that has a boyfriend. 1st it was amber, which we had a thing which was pretty big, and she never could get over rey, so that sucked. and that guy treated her like shit. and for real like real bad. but whatever. and now she got over rey and is with another guy. how ironic? but shit usually happens that way with me? i guess its kind of funny. 
then jena. well she had stopped talking to diego, and i thought she didnt like him ne more. so we talked, well maybe she considers it not talking so i'll jus say more than friends. we went to the movies, held hands, she even told me she liked me. bad ass, everything good. then one day at cross country practice she said that she had to let me go, becuz she was gonna get back wit diego. wow soo much for everything going good. and i cant say shit but from what i've heard he treats her like shit too. 
ok and now the more recent one. which some of u'll know. i wont mention her name becuz maybe she dont want me talking about her. so i'll just tell u'll what happened. she broke up with her boyfriend. i was talking to her. had bad ass conversations on the phone. and i mean bad ass. we didnt talk long but those short conversations were bad ass. then one night i call her to tell her goodnight, and as soon as she answers the phone she says i'll call you back. i asked her what you doing. and she said watching a movie with her ex-boyfriend. i was pretty tired so i thought i didnt hear right  so i just said goodnight and went to sleep becuz i had cross country in the morning. so go to cross country, then tennis, sleep, then open gym. o yeh o yeh. this is happening today, and we had already planned to go out on a date. ok now i call her after open gym. and i say, last night did u say you were watching a movie with ur ex. she was all yeh, he came over. then i asked so... are you back with him? she said yeh. right then and there my heart dropped, then somone was walking by and stepped on it. lol not funny but i'm trying to make the best out of things. then she says still friends...? and i say yeh not wanting to talk... can't even speak. speechless.
so basically waht i'm trying to say about everything is...i got bad luck with the ladies. maybe since its my senior year i should jus chill and concentrate on sports and school. thats what my parents say. but i'll tell u'll this much. i did like her, the recent girl. i though i was actually gonna have something serious, but i was mistaken again.
alright the other aspects of my life i'm running cross country. i hate it becuz i have to run and i get tired. obviously. lol but damn we work out a lot. and i'm also playing tennis. i've been playing for i think a month now, and its bad ass. its been alot of fun, and i mean a lot of fun. i wish i could jus play that but my coach for basketball is the same for cross country. so i kinda have to. i've jus recently joined golf so hopefully that will be fun too. lol. i'm doing a lot of sports right? lol but its bad ass. yeh well hopefully someone read this journal entry because i wrote a lot and that would suck if no one read it. lol alright then bye and i hope every is having good lives and keeps having good lives. bye

i'm here at my godfather's house. his mother just passed away. even though i didnt know her that much i'm going to miss her. everything has been going good for me. summer was bad ass and now skool is here. i dont like skool, but its all good. my last year in high school. thats freakin' crazy i dont care what ne one else says that's crazy. i read jeannie's journal. why wuz it a bummer that sumone mentioned me. wow i havent talked to you in a long time. i havent had my cpu for 2 months already so i cant get online no more. sorry guys. its been a real bummer not talking to everyone. and stephanie i know your mad at me. but our friendship, you not talking to me because i didnt sit with you that's kinda dumb. i think we'd be kooler enough for you not to let that get to you. but its alright i guess. so right now i'm running cross country and playing tennis. tennis is bad ass. at first it looked not fun, but playing it is bad ass. wut else....? well i just wanted to let you'll know how i'm doing. but to bad i cant read any of u'll reply's or maybe if i get online here at my godfather's again. yup yup. but as for now bye. and jeannnie. what's up niaaaaaaaaaga!!! lol. i barley read your poem. i liked it for real. thanx for being there with everything. and yeh just thanx. good bye everyone!!!

nothing really happened today. we had a game and lost gotcho. but fuck it its over. i did good though bt we lost so it dont matter. so nothing really eventfull happened today. but besides that its raining outside and i kind of like rain. yeh its kool

last night was weird. peter was talking to laura and i was just there listing, hearing them and wishing i had someone like that. u know one of those moments you see a guy and a girl talking just about ne thing having a good conversation and you think to urself damn i want something like that. well yeh that's what i had.

so out of now where there is a call on the other line. says out of area. so peter flashes over and it's someone i'd rather not say becuz she's paranoid about her boyfriend gettin mad at her. so we talk for a pretty long time just catching up and stuff. but i dunno it was nice talking to her. but with me and her its wierd because we both like eacother but something always happens to make us stop talking or something like that. but we talked like 3 hours. it was pretty good.

today woke up at 12. didnt go to practice at 8 for the 3rd straight time. i dunnno its just excuse after excuse. hopefully i'll get my ass up and go tomorrow. 

be ne ways. went to open gym at east and i played pretty good. then i went home. then in an hour matt comes to pick me up for our game at 6:30 and we're off.

the game went good. i did alright. but the freakin' 2nd team sucked. get this... we were up by 12 and me and javi (fellow player) get out of the game and they get outscored 15-2 in 5 minutes, 5 freakin minutes. oh my lord it pissed me off. so we're down by 1 with 10 minutes to go. and finally we end up winning the game by 1 point. ain't that craaazy!!! yup

so ne ways tomorrow hopefully i get to go out. i have kind of a date. but i dont know if you can call it a date. i dunno its weird. but hopefully tomorrow goes good wutever might happen. hopefully nothing bad happens and it turns into a shitty day.

yeh but i wrote a freakin' lot. that's a first but yeh prolly boring you'll already so i guess i'll cut if off here.                         
                                                    L a T e

hey i haven't written in this thing in a long time. i guess its cuz. i dunno. its 1 o' clock and i woke up 30 minutes ago. last weekend was bad ass. i went with peter and roman to the beach. it was bad ass. yesterday i had a game and we lost but i played good. yup, this summer is going good. hopefully it will get better. i think it will. alright. bye.

sup niaaaaaaaagas!!! me today was pretty kool. i thought there was gonna be open gym today at east, but it turned out there wasn't so that sucked. i didnt play ball the whole day. ain't that craaaazy. i think so. yup. so i went to the mall with mike. let me tell you that guy is a crazy spender. and my friend works at buckle so she hooked us up. she's bad ass. yeh then we got to mike's house and gabby rt gabby's sis forgot her name and yeh jus there doing nothing. it was pretty dumb. then they left and me and mike had a little pool tournament. let me tell you'll i was on freakin' fueeeeego. i was playing bad ass and beat him 5-2. what is up now.       i'm tooooooooooooooooooo damn good!!!! lol j/k yeh but that was my day. ne ways got a game tomorrow at 12. so holla back

damn yesterday i got in at night, and i think i lost my voice. i sound all sexy now. aww na hell na!!! lol. yup. so this morning woke up at 7:30 again to go to prac at 8. it wasnt as hard as yesterdays. i'm still feeling freakin' sore, like i walked like i got ganbanged in the ass. for real. lol but yeh. we had a game tonight, and lost by i think 7. i was super mad. i was even gettin mad at my teamates tellin' them off and stuff. man i'm so rude. lol but na i shouldn't of done that. fuck it two tears in the bucket. yeh so now i'm at home eating my mcdonalds. and bout to get in the shower. i hope tomorrow is bad ass. holla at me dogg hey ya'll hey ya'll. lol yeh. Now this gon' be the hardest thing I think I ever had to do.Got me talkin' to myself askin' how I'm gon' tell you. always got to be usher. lol see ya definatley would not want to be ya.

hey wut's up! lol like i'm talking to someone. its 9 :48 and i'm watchin the game. it seems like the lakers are gonna win because there doing good. i really dont care cuz i wanted the kings to go. damn kings didnt make it. yeh. today in the morning was so hurtfull on my piernas. damn i'm freakin sore right now. i wish someone, no wait, some girl could massage them. that would be freakin' awesome. o yeh guys jeannie asked me out. lol i know its suppose to be the guy be she did it. i dont know if i was suppose to tell you'll but i did. yesssssssssssss sirrrrrrrrrs and maaaaaaaaaaams. aight then i'm out like a flashlight without batteries. o yeh i dont know if its right for me to say this, but its coming from the heart.............................................. ahhh usher up in this biaaaatch. whoever thought i was gonna say something ya'll got punk'd! holla

hey! i'm gonna start off with this journal with i think jeannie is better off witout me. i read her journal and it seems she's having sooo much fun without me you know, like i was the one bringing her down. but i'm happy for her. i was at pizza hut, and our waiter reminded me of jeannie. it was weird. she was hott too. lol but yeh. ne ways. i had a workout at 8 o' clock in the morning. it was crazy but ne thing to get me stronger. i also had a game. we won by 20 we played as a team, it was bad ass. yeh but that was it for today. i'll try to keep writing in thsi journal. holla front, i mean back!!! 
G'night & Sweet Dreams!!!!

sup everyone. well this morning i woke up at 7 30 because i had a a game at 9 in mcallen. i played good it was bad ass cuz we won. then we played at 12 30 and lost by 1. the two games that we lost this weekend was by 1. so that sux. now i'm watching the pistons lakers game. its alright. pistons won but my kings aren't in it so i dont give a fizzzzzzuck my nizzzzuck. so damn nothing else to say. G'nite & Sweet Dreams!!!

yeh well today was kool. i woke up at 8 because i had a tournament, the first game we sucked and lost by a free throw. and we won the second game i played good. i also bought these bad ass shorts. their kool.i dont know what i'm gonna do tonite, i hope something fun. there is this recital that almost all my friends are in, but its up to peter if he wants to go. its funny how jeannie moved on so fast when she told me she liked me a lot. i dunno i just find that weird. and she's callin me a liar also. damn i didnt know i did ne thing wrong.

hey! i guess i'm back. maybe i'll start writing in this again! its not like my stories are interesting but watever. i realized that i wasted my whole time at the end of the school year worrying about passing and blocking everyone out. and now i have no one. its funny but i guess i deserve it. i guess me and jeannie are just friends now. i have to admit i did like her, but i was always too busy. if she reads this i'm sorry and should've made time. but i guess everything happens for a reason. now i'm jus wit my boy peter. and i'm taking summer skool at night. it sux. once i'm done then my real summer starts. so for now i guess i'll leave it there.

"everything happens for a a reason, but once that reason comes, everything will happen"

that's a true quote by Josh Rico 21

the lakers won the game. i really didnt care who won the game but the lakers pulled it off. i jus want the freakin kings to win the game tomorrow well today (Sunday) i think they play today. today i'm gonna make my Confirmation. it should be good, and i didnt go to Austin for a basketball tournament cause of my comitment to it. so hopefully everything turns out good. happy birthday carla well 55 mins ago but at least i said it. and o yeh, i feel like i'm getting further away from jeannie. ever since she asked me that question about how i feel. i mean i like her, but we hardly talk to i do not know what's gonna happen there. whatever happens happens you know, i can't control what's destined for me in the future. well to everyone               GooDnIghT & SWeeT DreAms!!!
things with basketball are going good, but i havent heard or talked to jeannie in 2 days. i wonder what is up! if she reads this i'm gonna be at confirmation prac today. call me like at 9!

hey! today was alright. skool sucked as usual. during 6th period my ankle hurt bad out of no where. i have no idea what it was. then at open gym i could hardly run. we had a game tonite. i could hardly play cuz i wuz hurt. i had like 6 or 8 points. damn we went into double overtime and lost with a last second buzzer shot. i hate those. then after i went home and got dressed and went to isaac's game at the church. after words i took him out to eat cuz it was his birthday. and i'm a nice guy like that. lol. but the thing that bothers me about today is jeannie. i mean i told her i liked her and yet she still is confused about how i feel. like if i'm lying or something. i dont know i thought relationships are based on trust. but i dunnnnno. and then she says that she was dissapointed with my journal. i mean i did care about that night. i jus dont go to tell the whole world in my live journal that's all. i mean what happens with us is with us. not everyone. i guess i'm just a differnt person. but i gotta go. to end this journal off in a good note 
H A P P Y B I R T H D A Y I S A A C ! ! !

hey! friday did not do jack shit. lol i had a game and we won. saturday i went to a 3 on 3 little tournament in La Feria at 9:30 in the freakin' morning. but we got second, so it was kool. but they hardly passed me the freakin' rock. fuck it. then i got back and went ninite! that was bad ass. then i woke up. and went to carmike to watch van helsing with jeannie. the movie was alright, but i didnt really like it. but being with jeannie was bad ass. our kiss was bad ass. lol. then sunday i went to church, slept, then shot around here at my house and thats about it. my weekend was alrite. HoLLa!!!

today i took my us history ap exam. it was alright. i hope i did good. then after that i ate chinese then went home. i fell alseep and then matt calls me saying our game is gonna start in 5 minutes. i got my shit and rushed to the game. i got in when the 2nd team was subing in. damn i was lucky. lol. i played good. i forgot to tell jeannie what time my game was but she still went. even though she got there late it was the thought that counts. i played with with another team and also did good. then i gave jeannie a sweaty kiss. it would've been on the lips but i was freakin' sweaty bad. i'm surprised she even let me kiss her. but it was kool. hopefully we go out tomorrow. i mean today. right now i just got through watchin' "The Last Samurai." it was a bad ass movie. now its 3:40 and i'm finally gonna go to bed. i'm tired. aight well g'nite to all of you'll and sweet dreams

today was alright. right now i'm listenin to yellowcard - empty apartment... call me out you stayed inside, one you love is where you hide. i love that song!!! well i had a game today for the church, but we lost. it sux cuz we always do bad in that leauge. but i'm gonna try my ass off in the tournament coming up. tomorrow i got my history ap exam. hopefully i do good. jeannie is taking the test also. hopefully she does good too!!! my game is at 7 or 8:30 just in case u'll want to go. so today wuz kool when i was talking to jeannie. hopefully i get to see her this weekend. peter says we're gonna watch "Van Helsinc" or however u spell it. but yup. well aight. holla front. i mean back.
